Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們光明正大的走出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.77,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是昨天那批人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你再接近勝海舟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.72,0:02:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十話\N沒有結尾的幕末\N上天給予海舟的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.02,0:02:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒必要為旁人\N讓自己的生命置於危險之中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你們是來者不善了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 知道勝先生面臨這樣的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不可能置之不管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.24,0:02:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別人的忠告你應該誠心接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連名字都不敢報的人的忠告\N我無意多聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今 已經不需要報名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想裝蒜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不准你說\N你不曉得「紅葵」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海舟沒跟你說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.33,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你不是勝海舟僱用的人 那就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也不想多做無益的殺生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不用多刺探了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 這樣就讓你累倒\N你想學功夫還早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個大頭小子挺努力的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 他確實很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概我是被熱昏了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 各位 飯煮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 不准比我先吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少嘍唆 快的人先吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人完全沒有破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可能原本就是武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生 您也來吃飯呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 讓我幫你提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了 你先去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飯後收拾也是一種修行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只說\N逸子跟大五郎拜託你了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.94,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只從他口中聽到這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.24,0:05:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的荷包蛋\N太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還給我\N好痛 住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.52,0:05:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛋是我特別留下來的\N可惡 你這小偷 滾回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.62,0:05:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你住手沒聽到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 還是回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐你還是回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.53,0:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師嘴上說歸說\N其實是擔心小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且老師自己一個人\N沒人煮飯給他吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係這對爸爸是個好教訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼努力讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是好事 你的劍術進步的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子小姐就會離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.56,0:06:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她還在這裏的一天\N我們就有好食物可吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.07,0:06:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們小姐做的有點難吃\N你也這麼認為吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連快餓死的貓都不想吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是這麼想 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有可以讓我們小姐\N看了就手藝變好的書？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我介紹打架變強的書\N啊 我不是看書的料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是一輩子的打架呆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你在看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵 會分散注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.53,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥他對科學有興趣\N我就借我的書給他看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣 大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.55,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近勝先生\N有沒有什麼不同的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同的地方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生在西南戰爭時\N給西鄉軍資金援助？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.24,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府好像是這樣懷疑他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西鄉隆盛是跟勝海舟一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.75,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,促成江戶無血開城的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.11,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可說是因為這兩人的會談\N而使江戶免於遭受戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會座時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西鄉隆盛保證\N停止隔天對江戶城的總攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對老師這麼說過：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算會遭受到許多阻止與議論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.51,0:08:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是會一肩擔下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西鄉這個人\N應該是個大人物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.49,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師在查問的官員離開後\N這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很想幫助西鄉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我辦不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在還不能死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是說我貪生怕死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是 我還有待辦之事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那個事結束之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的幕末時代是不會結束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.59,0:09:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把上一個時代的麻煩事\N留給我這個老頭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.96,0:09:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟鐵馬這種年輕人\N只要朝向未來前進就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是新時代了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說過這種話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.58,0:09:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直受逸子小姐和老師照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻無法報答他們恩情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼努力的讀書\N待在這裏好好修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以算是報恩不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這本書也是老師給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以上月球的那本？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫了很多寶貴的科學知識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.55,0:09:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了報答恩情\N我一定要使我的劍術進步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.52,0:10:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感人哦\N想要變強來保護勝海舟老爺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就算發生\N像上次那樣被攻擊的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也能挺身保護了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那些流氓般的人\N他們是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些武士至今仍然怨恨老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.27,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認為他是不戰而降\N把江戶讓給薩長軍的叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.18,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙像是有真本領的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒帶殺氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個自大的傢伙一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說撤就撤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.98,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近你來得很頻繁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擔心老師嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.10,0:11:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為軍需金的事情\N政府還在懷疑老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.67,0:11:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以為那些錢\N是老天爺飄下來給我的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府那邊的聲音\N我會壓制下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對上次那些歹徒發佈通緝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.02,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師\N待在這裏不是太危險了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.89,0:12:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時轉移到安全的地方如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到哪裏都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死的時候就會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會保護老師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 但是我無意離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這麼可靠的徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣聰明的人很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.56,0:12:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把我的思想與經驗\N全部教給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是還有大五郎在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.97,0:13:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不行 他什麼也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會說一些夢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 這就是他的優點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子也去那個道場\N不再回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她喜歡那裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…我可以去接她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.26,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子還不知世事\N就讓她在那裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是你\N在這裏浪費時間可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你確實幹什麼事都很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.75,0:13:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不可以自信過度哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.19,0:13:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心別太過自信\N而錯估了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.09,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天爺全部都看在眼裏的\N這個你要謹記在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我跟大五郎比賽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒閒時間一直揮棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題\N你有努力學習的氣魄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且資質也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 以初學者而言不錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥不能再鬆懈下去嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.03,0:14:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛\N你說我會輸給這軟弱的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.27,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 這對禰彥太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且今天我累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油了 大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.06,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？咦？喂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用氣魄贏他 大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腰…閃到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎 你怎麼了\N振作點 別死呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.04,0:16:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使看來脆弱~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.29,0:16:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要意志像石頭一樣堅硬~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.27,0:16:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霜柱草~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.95,0:16:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還痛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕鬆多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我覺得自己真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說這什麼話呀 大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.56,0:16:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 聽說霜柱草\N那小子閃到腰了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.33,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只要吃個驚\N讓腰再閃回來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 逸子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.11,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 請你住手呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說要做的人是你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏做什麼 快進…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要回去老師身邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.19,0:17:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑我的功夫\N可能要花上二三十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…又不是在報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.36,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你辦得到的 我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.97,0:17:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人都神經粗得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個行動決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不能選擇手段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.70,0:18:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了達成目的\N採取卑鄙的措施是不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有錢 我什麼都干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.07,0:18:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是為了錢才行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘記紅葵真正目的了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜行動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我自己動用廚房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.23,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒什麼\N我是敬佩得看呆了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個只要稍微學習\N任何人都會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼做都做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要做好 不知道\N要花上十年還是二十年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.51,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講話跟某人好像\N這很簡單的 讓我教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.21,0:19:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好\N我不會再讓左之助嫌難吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 你想做好的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是給左之助\N是想做緋村吃的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.06,0:19:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 逸子你跟大五郎怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.73,0:19:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是家父的徒弟嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼是為了叫鐵馬的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.48,0:19:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬確實是家父的弟子中\N最有出息的人 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有出息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人很自大\N給人感覺挺討厭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.97,0:20:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我想鐵馬是沒有惡意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.07,0:20:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他頭腦聰明劍術高強\N成為家父徒弟後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又努力的進入政府做事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.85,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實他是想為國家的未來\N做貢獻的正經人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 比起他來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.35,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是想搭大炮的彈丸\N上月球的人比較好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記菜頭了 我去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可叫禰彥做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.04,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 這個該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.32,0:21:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是勝海舟大人的千金\N逸子小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請跟我們同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來人呀 來人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼呀 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水呀 水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒、沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在馬上潑水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潑水？不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潑水會變成大火災\N不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.83,0:21:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他去買菜頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對我潑水幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 找東西來蓋住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.65,0:22:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！

